body:
This will first support uploads for spack monitor, and eventually could be used for other kinds of spack uploads. This PR can be reviewed in favor of #24317 as it also includes the fix.

@alecbcs this is likely what you want in favor of rolling your own interaction with the API. This also includes a bug fix that we need to save the temporary build id with the build metadata (to match to other results) instead of the spec hash.

Signed-off-by: vsoch <vsoch@users.noreply.github.com>
